OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1782496102
OL,3,CFire crews continue to tackle 500m
OL,4,Cwildfire on moorland near Glossop
OL,6,FDrone footage from Derbyshire Mountain
OL,7,FRescue Team is being live streamed
OL,8,Fdirectly to the fire service to help
OL,9,Fidentify hotspots.
OL,11,FFirefighters are battling a wildfire
OL,12,Fon moorlands just outside Greater
OL,13,FManchester.
OL,15,FEmergency services were called out to
OL,16,FTintwistle Moor near Glossop this
OL,17,Fafternoon, with around 500 square
OL,18,Fmetres alight.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
