PN,36402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1782496102
OL,3,CFire crews continue to tackle 500m
OL,4,Cwildfire on moorland near Glossop
OL,6,FSix fire engines are tackling the
OL,7,Fblaze and a helicopter from United
OL,8,FUtilities is being used to drop water
OL,9,Fto try and extinguish it.
OL,11,FCrews are expected to remain at the
OL,12,Fscene overnight, with people being
OL,13,Furged to avoid the area.
OL,15,FResidents who live close-by are being
OL,16,Fadvised to keep their windows and
OL,17,Fdoors shut.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
