OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,365,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1782496102
OL,3,CFire crews continue to tackle 500m
OL,4,Cwildfire on moorland near Glossop
OL,6,FA spokesperson for Derbyshire Fire and
OL,7,FRescue Service said: "Firefighters
OL,8,Ffrom Derbyshire and Greater Manchester
OL,9,Fare continuing to tackle the fire and
OL,10,Fare expected to remain on scene into
OL,11,Fthe night.
OL,13,F"Six fire engines are in attendance
OL,14,Fsupported by a high volume pump,
OL,15,Fcommand support unit, water carrier,
OL,16,Fmoorland vehicles and a helicopter
OL,17,Ffrom United Utilities which is being
OL,18,Fused to drop water onto the fire.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,365,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1782496102
OL,3,CFire crews continue to tackle 500m
OL,4,Cwildfire on moorland near Glossop
OL,6,F"The fire is affecting approximately
OL,7,F500 square metres of moorland and
OL,8,Fwoodland. Wildfires like this require
OL,9,Fa huge response and people are asked
OL,10,Fto keep this in mind as the warm
OL,11,Fweather continues.
OL,13,F"The ground is tinder dry and the
OL,14,Fslightest spark from a campfire, a
OL,15,Ftiny burning ember from a BBQ, or a
OL,16,Fflake of ash from a discarded
OL,17,Fcigarette could soon escalate to a
OL,18,Fmajor incident so please act
OL,19,Fresponsibly."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,365,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1782496102
OL,3,CFire crews continue to tackle 500m
OL,4,Cwildfire on moorland near Glossop
OL,6,FA statement from the Derby Mountain
OL,7,FRescue Team reads: "Our drone section
OL,8,Fis currently deployed in support of
OL,9,FDerbyshire Fire & Rescue Service at a
OL,10,Flarge wildfire near Glossop.
OL,12,F"Live aerial footage from the drone is
OL,13,Fbeing streamed directly to the
OL,14,FDerbyshire Fire & Rescue Service
OL,15,Fcommand vehicle, providing real-time
OL,16,Fsituational awareness to help inform
OL,17,Foperational decision-making and the
OL,18,Fdeployment of resources.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
