PN,36406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1782496102
OL,3,CFire crews continue to tackle 500m
OL,4,Cwildfire on moorland near Glossop
OL,6,F"We'd ask members of the public to
OL,7,Favoid the area where possible and to
OL,8,Ffollow any advice issued by the
OL,9,Femergency services while crews
OL,10,Fcontinue to work at the scene."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/6
